          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">B</hi>Eneath this verdant <hi rend="italics">hillock</hi> lies,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-2" n="2">Demar, the <hi rend="italics">wealthy</hi> and the <hi rend="italics">wise</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-3" n="3">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-4" n="4">om.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-5" n="5">His <hi rend="italics">heirs</hi>, that he might safely rest,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-6" n="6">Have put his <hi rend="italics">carcase</hi> in a <hi rend="italics">chest</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-7" n="7">The very <hi rend="italics">chest</hi>, in which, they say,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-8" n="8">His <hi rend="italics">other self</hi>, his <hi rend="italics">money</hi>, lay.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-9" n="9">And, if his <hi rend="italics">heirs</hi> continue kind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-10" n="10">To that dear <hi rend="italics">self</hi> he left behind,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-11" n="11">I dare believe, that four in five</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-235-06E2-line-12" n="12">Will think his <hi rend="italics">better half</hi> alive.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
